## Threat Modeling (STRIDE)

### STRIDE Analysis per Komponen

| # | Aset / Proses | Threat | STRIDE Category | Severity | Mitigation |
|---|---------------|--------|-----------------|----------|------------|
| T1 | JWT Auth (`/auth/login`) | Token tidak expire / reuse setelah logout | **Spoofing** | 🔴 High | Token blacklist (Redis), set `exp` ketat |
| T2 | JWT Secret Key | Hardcoded secret di `.env` tanpa rotation | **Information Disclosure** | 🔴 High | Secrets manager (Vault/AWS SSM), env rotation |
| T3 | `/payments/webhook` | Signature verification di-comment → fake webhook bisa diterima | **Tampering** | 🔴 Critical | Aktifkan `verify_webhook_signature()`, HMAC-SHA512 |
| T4 | `/concerts` CRUD | Admin endpoint tidak ada rate limit → brute force / DoS | **Denial of Service** | 🟠 Medium | Rate limiting (slowapi), NGINX throttle |
| T5 | Database PostgreSQL | Port 5432 exposed ke publik di docker-compose | **Information Disclosure** | 🔴 High | Hapus port expose, hanya internal Docker network |
| T6 | QR Code ticket | QR tidak cryptographically signed → bisa dipalsukan | **Spoofing / Tampering** | 🟠 Medium | Sign QR payload dengan HMAC + blockchain anchor |
| T7 | CORS (`allow_origins`) | Saat ini hanya `localhost:3000` — kurang ketat di production | **Spoofing** | 🟡 Low-Med | Whitelist domain production secara eksplisit |
| T8 | SQL Injection | SQLAlchemy ORM digunakan, tapi raw query berpotensi ada | **Tampering** | 🟠 Medium | SAST scan, parameterized query only |
| T9 | Dependency Vulnerabilities | `python-jose 3.3.0`, `passlib 1.7.4` — versi lama | **Elevation of Privilege** | 🟠 Medium | OWASP Dependency-Check, update berkala |
| T10 | Broken Access Control | Tidak ada role-check konsisten di semua endpoint | **Elevation of Privilege** | 🔴 High | Middleware role-based access control (RBAC) |
| T11 | Docker secrets | `.env` commit risiko, secret di container env | **Information Disclosure** | 🟠 Medium | Docker Secrets / `.env` excluded di `.gitignore` |
| T12 | Ticket Scalping / Double-use | QR dapat di-screenshot dan digunakan berulang | **Tampering** | 🔴 High | Blockchain immutable ledger untuk mark "used" |

