## Minggu 3 — Blockchain Ticketing (STASH & DASH)

### Arsitektur Blockchain untuk Tiket

**Konsep:** Setiap tiket yang dibeli akan dibuatkan **Block** yang berisi hash dari data tiket. Block-block ini berantai membentuk **immutable ledger** untuk mencegah double-use / pemalsuan.

```
Block N = {
  "index": N,
  "timestamp": "...",
  "ticket_id": "uuid",
  "user_id": "uuid",
  "concert_id": "uuid",
  "qr_hash": "sha256(...)",
  "previous_hash": "abc123...",
  "hash": "def456..."
}
```

### Implementasi (Lightweight, tanpa external blockchain)

**Pilihan:** Simple in-house blockchain di PostgreSQL (sesuai skala akademis)

#### [NEW] `backend/app/models/blockchain.py`
- Model `Block` dengan fields: `index`, `timestamp`, `data`, `previous_hash`, `hash`, `nonce`

#### [NEW] `backend/app/services/blockchain_service.py`
- `add_ticket_block(ticket_id, user_id, concert_id)` — tambah block baru
- `verify_chain_integrity()` — validasi seluruh chain
- `get_ticket_block(ticket_id)` — cari block by ticket

#### [MODIFY] `backend/app/routers/tickets.py`
- Setelah pembayaran sukses → panggil `add_ticket_block()`

#### [NEW] `backend/app/routers/blockchain.py`
- `GET /blockchain/chain` — lihat seluruh chain
- `GET /blockchain/verify` — verifikasi integritas
- `GET /blockchain/ticket/{ticket_id}` — cek status blockchain tiket

#### [MODIFY] `docker-compose.yml`
- Tambah `grafana`, `prometheus`, `redis`, `sonarqube` services

